data.description: Step into this beautifully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that seamlessly blends modern elegance with functionality. Step onto brand-new floors that add a touch of luxury to each room, creating a cohesive and modern aesthetic. Inside, the beautiful floors throughout the living spaces offer a classic touch, while the tile in the wet spaces offer functionality. Together they create a warm and inviting atmosphere. Imagine preparing meals in a space adorned with quartz countertops, complemented by sleek stainless-steel appliances. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the stunning kitchen, where style meets practicality. it's a culinary haven that inspires creativity.It has an excellent remodeled bathroom that is accessible. This property presents an exciting opportunity to create the perfect home in an enviable location. Don't miss the chance to turn this into your dream retreat. Schedule a showing today and envision the endless possibilities this property holds. The outdoor space is transformed into a serene garden, offering a tranquil retreat for relaxation or outdoor gatherings. The roof replaced before de closing date, while the updated HVAC system ensures comfort throughout the seasons. In summary, this remodeled gem is not just a house; it's a carefully curated living experience where every detail has been considered to create a harmonious blend of comfort, style, and modern convenience.
